OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPM sets out pothole funding
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom HS2 savings           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Prime Minister Rishi Sunak has set out 
OL,6, how #8.3bn of promised funding will be 
OL,7, used to tackle what he called the      
OL,8, "scourge of potholes".                 
OL,10,FThe PM announced the money last month  
OL,11,Fas part of plans to scrap part of the  
OL,12,FHS2 high-speed rail line and spend the 
OL,13,Fsavings on other projects.             
OL,15,FThe funding will go to England's local 
OL,16,Fcouncils over the next 11 years for    
OL,17,Froad maintenance.                      
OL,19,FCouncils said the cost of repairing    
OL,20,Flocal roads was closer to #14bn.       
